Note on referenced resources
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

This dataset references entries of the following resources, which are
governed by their own respective licenses and terms of use:

- Standard Disease Master (標準病名マスター) v5.04
    provided by MEDIS-DC.
- ICD-11 (International Classification of Diseases, 11th Revision)
    provided by the World Health Organization (WHO).

Users of this dataset must comply with the terms of use of the above
resources when they make use of the referenced codes / URIs.
